'''''Polyhedron'' 99''' was a roleplaying magazine from [[September]] of [[1994]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including a rules supplement for the [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game|D6]] system. The article was called "[[Lightsabers: And the Force in the Star Wars New Republic]]" and was written by [[Bill Slavicsek]] and [[Michele Carter]]. Like all supplements printed in ''[[Polyhedron]]'' prior to [[2002]], the article is considered ambiguously [[canon]].

